Create and Share CRM Analytics for Financial Services Apps

Follow these general steps to create and share the apps included in CRM Analytics for Financial Services. These include Analytics for Wealth Management, Predict Client Churn Risk for Wealth Management Analytics, Predict Likelihood to Add Assets for Wealth Management Analytics, Analytics for Insurance, Analytics for Retail Banking, Wealth Starter Analytics, Analytics for Mortgage, or Consumer Banking Starter Analytics.

Navigate to Analytics Studio.
Click Create, then select App.
Select the template for the app you want to create:
Then click Continue.
Have a quick look at the template preview page, then click Continue to open the configuration wizard.
CRM Analytics performs a compatibility check of your org’s data. If it uncovers any issues, you see error messages with instructions about how to address them.

Name your app something you and users can easily remember and click Create.
View the status of app creation on the next page. The process takes a minute or two. Once it's complete, refresh the page to see your app.

Now that you’ve created the app, share it with users in your organization. You can share it only with users assigned the admin or user permission sets for CRM Analytics for Financial Services.

Open your app if it’s not already open. Click the Share icon at upper right.
In the next screen, use the search field under Invite others: to find other users in your org.
Select whether you want to make the selected user a Viewer, Editor, or Manager of the app.
Click Add, then click Save.

Create and Share specific apps:
Create and Share the Analytics for Insurance App
Create and Share the Policy Renewal Prediction App
Create and Share the FSC Insurance Analytics Fast Start App
Create and Share the Einstein Discovery for Insurance Analytics App
Create and Share the Insurance Claims and Policy Analytics App
Create and Share the Analytics for Wealth Management App
Create and Share the Predict Client Churn Risk for Wealth Management Analytics App
Create and Share the Predict Likelihood to Add Assets for Wealth Management Analytics App
